{
  "texts": [
    "The dataset comprises a collection of heart sound recordings obtained from a sample size of 400 individuals.",
    "The participants were categorized into two groups: a group of 200 individuals with typical cardiac function and another group of 200 individuals with atypical cardiac function.",
    "The patients in the dataset were collected from four different clinical sites, each contributing an almost equal number of subjects.",
    "According to 32, the dataset encompasses a maximum of three recordings, each lasting approximately 10 seconds, for every subject.",
    "These recordings are obtained from distinct chest positions."
  ]
}